    "about_position": "<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"> <span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">We are looking for an individual to join our growing team at HELM in the capacity of Operations Support!</span><span style=\"color: #001e00; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\"> You will be working remotely with our client in the supplements (e-commerce) industry.</span></div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></strong><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;\">Requirements:</span>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Amazon/e-commerce experience is preferable (shipment/operations)</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Project management experience</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Supplement industry experience</span></li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Strong understanding of SOPs</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Exceptional verbal and written English skills (native English level)</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Willingness to learn</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Self driven with high initiative</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">You can handle pressure and a fast paced environment</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Very strong organizational and communication skills</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Impeccable attention to detail</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Fluency in Spanish is a plus!</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;\">Responsibilities:</span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Understanding/learning existing SOPs, helping implement new SOPs</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Assist with project management</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Organizing files/labeling</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Create shipments</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Liaise with other team members and contract manufacturers</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Inventory management</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Checking product labels (you enjoy details!)</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Check other team members&rsquo; work to ensure accuracy</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Various Amazon tasks&nbsp;</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Ad hoc operational tasks</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2;\"><span style=\"color: #001e00; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">As your work with our client evolves, so will your skillset and responsibilities.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;\">Location:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">Fully remote (contractor basis)</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;\">Weekly Hours:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">40hrs per week, within 9am to 5pm EST, with some occasional flexibility required</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;\">Pay Range:</span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\"> $11/hr (potentially +/- $2/hr)</span></p>\n<strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></strong><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">If you are interested in this opportunity, please submit your CV and share why!&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></strong>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; text-decoration: none;\">A bit about us... Helm is a staffing agency that exists to help people achieve freedom. You can learn more about this at our website or from our founder&rsquo;s podcast.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</div>",
