        "content": "<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Dragana Praiz wrote on April 12:</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong>Additional requirements</strong>: Logistics, supply chain and procurement management experience desirable (ingredient sourcing)</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Dragana Praiz wrote on April 11:</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Hapi Petrolla Jhustine Wong supplement industry experience is a must have - Josh was advised by the client today. Please adjust your search accordingly.</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Dragana Praiz wrote on April 5:</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Hapi Petrolla Jhustine Wong please note that we will assume that supplement industry experience is a 'nice-to-have', not a 'need-to-have', until Josh has discussed in more detail with the client.<!-- notionvc: 2d214678-f874-4063-ad8e-81de0e53dc0e --></div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Dragana Praiz wrote on Mar 21:</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Great - document your territories int he fields of this card. Tx</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Hapi Petrolla wrote on Mar 21:</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Jhustine Wong Dragana Praiz I am back in Upwor